elements.expression: CASE substring(ExtractValue(ajra,'//datafield[@tag="100"]/subfield[@code="a"]'),18,1) WHEN 'a'  THEN 'a-Jeunesse (gnral)' WHEN 'b' THEN 'b-Pr-scolaire' WHEN 'c' THEN 'c-Scolaire' WHEN 'd' THEN 'd-Enfant' WHEN 'e' THEN 'e-Jeune adulte' WHEN 'k' THEN 'k-Adulte haut niveau' WHEN 'm' THEN 'm-Adulte grand public' WHEN 'u' THEN 'u-Inconnu' ELSE '~-Invalide' END

elements.expression: CASE substring(ExtractValue(ajra,'//leader'),7,1)  WHEN 'a' THEN 'Doc textuel'  WHEN 'b' THEN 'Doc textuel manuscrit' WHEN 'c' THEN 'Partition' WHEN 'd' THEN 'Partition manuscrite' WHEN 'e' THEN 'Carte' WHEN 'f' THEN 'Carte manuscrite' WHEN 'g' THEN 'Vido' WHEN 'i' THEN 'Doc sonore non musical' WHEN 'j' THEN 'Doc sonore musical' WHEN 'k' THEN 'Image/Dessin' WHEN 'l' THEN 'Ress. lectronique' WHEN 'm' THEN 'Multimdia' WHEN 'r' THEN 'Objet en 3D' ELSE 'Non dfini' END
elements.viewExpression: CASE substring(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'),7,1)  WHEN 'a' THEN 'Doc textuel'  WHEN 'b' THEN 'Doc textuel manuscrit' WHEN 'c' THEN 'Partition' WHEN 'd' THEN 'Partition manuscrite' WHEN 'e' THEN 'Carte' WHEN 'f' THEN 'Carte manuscrite' WHEN 'g' THEN 'Vido' WHEN 'i' THEN 'Doc sonore non musical' WHEN 'j' THEN 'Doc sonore musical' WHEN 'k' THEN 'Image/Dessin' WHEN 'l' THEN 'Ress. lectronique' WHEN 'm' THEN 'Multimdia' WHEN 'r' THEN 'Objet en 3D' ELSE 'Non dfini' END

elements.expression: CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('am', 'ac','om')  THEN 'Livre imprim' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='as' THEN 'Revue imprime' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN('gm','gn','gs') THEN 'DVD' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='bm' THEN 'Manuscrit' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('jm', 'im' ,'jn') THEN 'CD' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='km' THEN 'Image fixe' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='em' THEN 'Carte imprime' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='cm' THEN 'Partition imprime' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('mm','ms') THEN 'Doc multimedia multisupport' WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#ajra,'//leader'), 7, 2)='lm' THEN 'Doc lectronique' ELSE 'Autre doc' END
